---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Spirit Media — A Global Team for a Global Mission"
  description="Meet the family behind Spirit Media. We walk with Kingdom Messengers from restoration to proclamation."
>
  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">About Us</p>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
          A Global Team for a Global Mission
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-red-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          We walk with Kingdom Messengers from restoration to proclamation — empowering them from
          heart → message → movement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===================== WHY WE EXIST ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why We Exist</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Spirit Media exists because the Good News was never meant to stop at borders. Too often,
          vision in publishing has been small, limited to markets instead of nations. But our
          Heavenly Father worthy of His story bearing fruit in all 195 nations of the earth. We
          exist to remove the barriers — the complexity, the cost, the confusion — and to equip
          Kingdom Messengers with the publishing and marketing solutions they need to multiply
          Kingdom impact and generational inheritance. What began as holy frustration became a
          global mandate. We are here to build sustainable Kingdom movements, amplify our
          Father’s heart, and see His whisper reach every tribe, tongue, and nation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===================== KEVIN AND SHELLY WHITE ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">

          <!-- Text column -->
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Kevin and Shelly White</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Kevin White is an author, speaker, and marketplace pastor with decades of experience
              planting churches, leading nonprofits, starting companies, and developing leaders
              worldwide. Together with his wife, Shelly, he co-founded and leads Spirit Media,
              Father’s Heart Bible&trade;, and Work On Yourself. As partners in both marriage and
              mission for nearly forty years, they are committed to empowering Kingdom Messengers.
              They live in North Carolina with their family.
            </p>

            <!-- Free Book CTA box -->
            <div class="bg-red-600 text-white rounded-xl p-8">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-2">
                FREE BOOK from Spirit Media
              </p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
                FATHER’S HEART → BELOVED IDENTITY
              </h3>
              <p class="text-red-100 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                Eight billion people are asking the same question: Who am I? Only one voice holds
                the answer. In this powerful compact devotional, your Heavenly Father speaks
                directly to you — revealing His heart, dismantling the orphan spirit, and
                establishing your true identity as His beloved child. Come home. You belong to Him.
              </p>
              <a
                href="https://fathersheartbible.com/join"
                class="inline-block bg-white text-red-700 font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors"
              >
                Get Your Free Copy →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Placeholder image column -->
          <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div
              class="w-full max-w-sm aspect-[3/4] bg-gray-200 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 text-lg font-medium"
            >
              Photo — Kevin &amp; Shelly White
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===================== MISSION & VISION ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">

          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3">Mission</p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed font-medium">
              We walk with Kingdom Messengers from restoration to proclamation. Empowering them
              from heart → message → movement.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-3">Vision</p>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed font-medium">
              For our Father’s heart to be poured out on His beloved sons and daughters in all
              195 nations.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===================== OUR VALUES ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Our Values</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Father’s Heart</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We seek to reveal the Father Heart of God in every relationship and decision.
              Everything flows from who God is as Father. We refuse orphan thinking. We build from
              intimacy, identity, and inheritance, not insecurity.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Faith</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We pursue bold vision, trusting our perfect and loving Heavenly Father for outcomes
              beyond our capacity. We move where vision requires dependence on God. If it can be
              done without Him, it isn’t big enough.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Family</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We build covenant relationships and treat every author, partner, and team member like
              family. We operate from covenants, not contracts. Honor and trust matters here.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Excellence</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Our Father deserves our best as we seek His best. We reject mediocrity. We refine,
              sharpen, improve, and elevate. From manuscript to marketplace, we steward every
              detail with intentionality.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Multiplication</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              We think nations, not numbers. We are not building for one launch or one market. We
              empower heart → message → movement that multiply across generations.
              The mandate is 195 nations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600 shadow-sm">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Stewardship</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
              Nothing entrusted to us is small. Messages carry eternity. Resources carry
              responsibility. Relationships carry legacy. We handle them with integrity, wisdom, and
              long-term Kingdom vision.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- ===================== OUR TEAM ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 text-center">Our Team</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">
          We are a global team for a global mission. Our team spans the USA, India, the
          Philippines, and beyond — because reaching 195 nations requires the best talent from
          more than one.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8">
          {[
            { initials: "KW", name: "Kevin and Shelly White", role: "CEO / Creative" },
            { initials: "AB", name: "Ana Marie Barrieses", role: "HR" },
            { initials: "DF", name: "David Foster", role: "Publishing" },
            { initials: "WP", name: "Walinda Phiri", role: "Marketing" },
            { initials: "JK", name: "Justin Keishing", role: "Events" },
            { initials: "JE", name: "Jay Esteban", role: "Production" },
            { initials: "ML", name: "Michele Lewis", role: "Production Team" },
            { initials: "GS", name: "Glory Suresh", role: "Production Team" },
            { initials: "SB", name: "Suresh Bob", role: "Production Team" },
            { initials: "VJ", name: "Vinit James", role: "Production Team" },
            { initials: "RT", name: "Revo Tribaco", role: "Production Team" },
            { initials: "KA", name: "Kali White", role: "Production Team" },
          ].map((member) => (
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-700 flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold flex-shrink-0">
                {member.initials}
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 leading-snug">{member.name}</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-0.5">{member.role}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===================== WHY PARTNER ===================== -->
    <section class="bg-[#050d1a] text-white py-24 px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Why Partner with Spirit Media?</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Our Father’s Heart is for relationships not just results. He offers significance not
          just success. Let Spirit Media be your long-term publishing partner to prioritize our
          Father’s heart → message → movement IN you while leaving His Work
          THROUGH you in His hands.
        </p>
        <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-red-600 pl-6 text-left mb-10 italic text-gray-300">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            “Seek our Father’s Kingdom above all else, and live righteously, and he will give
            you everything you need.”
          </p>
          <footer class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400 not-italic">— Matthew 6:33 (FHB)</footer>
        </blockquote>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors text-lg"
        >
          Request a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
